                </profile>
                <profile name="Buried Horrors" typeId="6a24-9ebc-0a52-315c" typeName="Abilities" hidden="false" id="b47e-d2df-b27c-a4f2">
                  <characteristics>
                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="48e9-7c24-9d42-a0b1">During deployment, instead of setting this unit up normally, place 3 1&quot; Buried tokens anywhere on the battlefield that is outside of the enemies deployment area, write down which token this unit is buried under. 


If a enemy unit ends their turn within 6&quot; of a Buried token, you may reveal and activate this unit, placing each model within 3&quot; of the buried token.

you may also chose to spend 2 AP to reveal this unit, placing each model within 3&quot; of the buried token.

If multiple units have this ability, more than 1 unit may not be assigned to each buried token, each unit after the first unit that activates this ability only places down 2 additional buried tokens</characteristic>
                  </characteristics>
                </profile>
              </profiles>
              <selectionEntryGroups>
                <selectionEntryGroup name="Melee Weapons" id="4006-b6f8-3984-d2ca" hidden="false" sortIndex="2">
